title: Photos: Rumoured TV Couple Chilling On The Beaches Of Thailand
text:
Swagata Dam Jan . 9 . 2017 
Popular TV actor Kunal Karan Kapoor is rumoured to be dating Sriti Jha aka Pragya from Kumkum Bhagya . And the duo was recently chilling in Thailand with their actor friends, Arjit Taneja and Leena Jumani . Here are some photos of their fun getaway. A photo posted by Kunal Karan Kapoor (@kunalkarankapoor) on Jan 8, 2017 at 7:19am PST A photo posted by Arjit Taneja (@arjitaneja) on Jan 1, 2017 at 3:52am PST A photo posted by Arjit Taneja (@arjitaneja) on Dec 29, 2016 at 2:27am PST A photo posted by Arjit Taneja (@arjitaneja) on Jan 4, 2017 at 1:56am PST A photo posted by Sriti Jha (@itisriti) on Jan 7, 2017 at 2:25am PST A photo posted by Charu Mehra (@4umehra) on Jan 4, 2017 at 4:17am PST A photo posted by Sriti Jha (@itisriti) on Jan 5, 2017 at 5:04am PST A photo posted by Leena Jumani (@leena_real) on Jan 2, 2017 at 3:11am PST 
Good times!
